title: The New Kim! Kylie Jenner Scores Spinoff Reality Show
text:
Move over, Kim ! Kardashian’s little sister Kylie Jenner has scored her very own spinoff reality show, RadarOnline.com can exclusively reveal.
“Kylie is so excited,” a source claimed, adding that the new series will focus on the 19-year-old Kylie Lip Kit creator’s growing empire. “It’s going to be all about building her business, and hiring people for her team.”
PHOTOS: Too Much Too Soon! Kylie Jenner’s Biggest Secrets & Scandals Explained In 10 Clicks! 
In addition to her cosmetics brands , Jenner recently launched a clothing and accessories line on The Kylie Shop.
Of course, the new series will air on Keeping Up With the Kardashians ’ E! network, the source said.
As Radar previously reported, the youngest Kardashian sibling has been gunning for her own show for years — and especially wanted to break free from her A-list supermodel sister Kendall’s shadow .
PHOTOS: Tyga Gives Kylie Jenner A $320,000 Ferrari For Her 18th Birthday – Plus, Kylie’s Major Wardrobe Malfunction 
“She wants the show to be all about her,” a source said in early 2016. “She no longer wants to do one with Kendall.”
